::Prowl/Striker::

Prowl turns to Rhinox. "A new base is kinda hard to build. I think we're 
stuck with this one."

At that point Striker walks by. "A maximal battle cruiser has just landed," 
he says to Prowl and the other maximals there, "Rhinox, can you come with me 
and check it out?"

Prowl blinks. What were the odds of that? He looks down at his scanner, 
looking at the position of the new ship.
